      <title>随着经济增长势头增强，德国商业前景改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/german-business-outlook-improves-with-economic-momentum-building</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业前景连续第四个月上升，因为人们对该国经济反弹将在今年剩余时间内加强的信心增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/german-business-outlook-improves-with-economic-momentum-building</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 08:05:50 GMT</pubDate>
